title: Ashes 2015 Live Blog Video Highlights 4th Test Trent Bridge Australia England | The
text:
FOLLOW live coverage of the fourth Test of the 2015 Ashes series in our over-by-over live blog as Australia and England do battle at Trent Bridge.
TIMELINE OF DISASTER
11:06am – Chris Rogers 0 caught Cook, bowled Broad. 1-4
11:09am – Steve Smith 6 caught Root, bowled Broad. 2-10
11:12am – David Warner 0 caught Buttler, bowled Wood. 3-10
11:20am – Shaun Marsh 2 caught Bell, bowled Broad. 4-15
11:28am – Adam Voges 1 caught Stokes, bowled Broad. 5-21
11:39am – Michael Clarke 10 caught Cook, bowled Broad. 5-29
Send in your questions to Steve Wilson at stephen.wilson@news.com.au
